OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,FA mother has called for more to be
OL,7,Fdone to stop drugs getting into HMP
OL,8,FParc after her son died from a
OL,9,Fsuspected spice overdose in the
OL,10,FBridgend prison.
OL,12,FIt comes as one former inmate who was
OL,13,Frecently released told ITV Wales that
OL,14,Fdrugs are as easy to get inside HMP
OL,15,FParc as a newspaper.
OL,17,F17 people have died at HMP Parc in
OL,18,Fthis year alone. Not all of those
OL,19,Fdeaths are drug-related but eight have
OL,20,Fbeen put down to non-natural causes.
