OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police has said the drug
OL,7,FNitazene, an opioid which can be many
OL,8,Ftimes stronger than heroin, has been
OL,9,Fconnected to four of the prisoners who
OL,10,Fhave died.
OL,12,FNitazenes have been known to have been
OL,13,Fmixed into spice, a synthetic drug
OL,14,Fmade to mimic the effects of cannabis.
OL,16,FAround 700 prison staff were trained
OL,17,Fto use the anti-opioid medicine
OL,18,Fnaloxone amid a spate of nine deaths
OL,19,Fin three months earlier this year.
