OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,FRyan Harding died from an apparent
OL,7,Foverdose on the synthetic drug spice a
OL,8,Fshort time after speaking to his mum
OL,9,FCatherine in January 2023. An inquest
OL,10,Finto his death is yet to take place.
OL,12,FCatherine says she was completely
OL,13,Funaware that her son was taking hard
OL,14,Fdrugs.
OL,16,FThe 26-year-old was coming to the end
OL,17,Fof an 18 month-sentence for causing
OL,18,Fcriminal damage and making threats to
OL,19,Fkill.
