OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,F"The last time I spoke to him was the
OL,7,Fday before he died," Catherine told
OL,8,FITV Wales.
OL,10,F"He said 'are you still sending me
OL,11,Fmoney, mam?' and 'I love you, mam'. I
OL,12,Fdidn't know that was the last time I
OL,13,Fwas going to hear from him."
OL,15,FCatherine said: "He only had seven
OL,16,Fweeks left (in prison) and he was
OL,17,Flooking forward to coming out and
OL,18,Fchanging his life.
OL,20,F"I don't understand it. I just don't
OL,21,Funderstand it at all.
