OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,F"I blame G4S and the prison (for
OL,7,FRyan's death) because they allowed
OL,8,Fdrugs to come into the prison.
OL,10,F"You go to the prison to visit
OL,11,Fsomebody and you're searched. Why
OL,12,Faren't the prison officers?
OL,14,F"That spice is lethal and if my son
OL,15,Fknew he would die he wouldn't have
OL,16,Ftaken it. Definitely not."
