OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,FG4S, the company which manages the
OL,7,Fprison, says security measures have
OL,8,Fbeen significantly strengthened,
OL,9,Fincluding an increase in the number of
OL,10,Fdedicated searching staff, patrol dogs
OL,11,Fand specialist equipment like drug
OL,12,Fdetection devices and X-ray body
OL,13,Fscanners.
OL,15,FIt added that, as with all closed
OL,16,Fprisons, Parc is fighting an ongoing
OL,17,Fbattle with organised crime groups who
OL,18,Fseek to traffic drugs into prisons
OL,19,Fusing various routes.
