OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,FNearly two years on from Ryan's death,
OL,7,Fone former prisoner who has been
OL,8,Frecently released from HMP Parc says
OL,9,Fspice is easy to get hold of when
OL,10,Fyou're inside and the drugs getting in
OL,11,Fleads to violence.
OL,13,F"I've witnessed people getting slashed
OL,14,For cut up, mainly over drugs", he told
OL,15,FITV Wales.
OL,17,F"If you go to a newsagents and get a
OL,18,Fnewspaper, (getting spice is) the same
OL,19,Fas that. It's widely available."
