OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,FA HMP Parc spokesperson said: "We send
OL,7,Four condolences to Ms Harding and the
OL,8,Fother families who have lost loved
OL,9,Fones.
OL,11,F"The majority of the allegations made
OL,12,Fby the ex-prisoner are categorically
OL,13,Fnot true.
OL,15,F"Significant effort and resources are
OL,16,Fused to tackle the supply of illegal
OL,17,Fdrugs and we work closely with South
OL,18,FWales Police to provide intelligence
OL,19,Fand evidence.
