OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,F"The vast majority of our staff are
OL,7,Fhonest and hard working. In the rare
OL,8,Fcases where staff are found to have
OL,9,Fbeen engaged in wrongdoing, robust
OL,10,Faction is taken, up to and including
OL,11,Fprosecution.
OL,13,F"We have worked at pace this year on
OL,14,Fsix key areas - staffing, safety,
OL,15,Fsecurity, drugs, regime and respect.
OL,16,FOutcomes are improving in these areas.
OL,17,FIncidents of violence have fallen
OL,18,Fsignificantly between April and
OL,19,FOctober 2024."
