OL,3,C'I blame the prison' - Mum calls for
OL,4,Cmore drug searches after son's death
OL,6,FThey added: "The key routes for drug
OL,7,Fingress are drones and people
OL,8,Fattempting to bring contraband in
OL,9,Fduring visits. All visitors to the
OL,10,Fprison are searched.
OL,12,F"We actively counter the risk of staff
OL,13,Fbringing contraband into the prison.
OL,14,FFor example, in October, over 1,500
OL,15,Fsearches were carried out on members
OL,16,Fof staff, including entry searches and
OL,17,Fnight searches."
